quran[10{c,v,t}:
21,1,Iqtaraba linnaasi hisaa buhum wa hum fee ghaflatim mu'ridoon
21,2,Maa yaateehim min zikrim mir Rabbihim muhdasin illas tama'oohu wa hum yal'aboon
21,3,Laahiyatan quloobuhum; wa asarrun najwal lazeena zalamoo hal haazaa illaa basharum mislukum afataa toonas sihra wa antum tubsiroon
21,4,Qaala Rabbee ya'lamul qawla fis samaaa'i wal ardi wa Huwas Samee'ul Aleem
21,5,Bal qaalooo adghaasu ahlaamim balif taraahu bal huwa shaa'irun falyaatinaa bi Aayatin kamaa ursilal awwaloon
21,6,Maaa aaamanat qablahum min qaryatin ahlaknaahaa a-fahum yu'minoon
21,7,Wa maaa arsalnaa qablaka illaa rijaalan nooheee ilaihim fas'aloo ahlaz zikri in kuntum laa ta'lamoon
21,8,Wa maa ja'alnaahum jasadal laa yaakuloonat ta'aama wa maa kaanoo khaalideen
21,9,summa sadaqnaa humul wa'da fa-anjainaahum wa man nashaaa'u wa ahlaknal musrifeen
21,10,Laqad anzalnaaa ilaikum Kitaaban feehi zikrukum afalaa ta'qiloon
